          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ClickUp",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and the shift has been nothing short of transformative. This platform genuinely lives up to its promise of being an all-in-one work hub. In this tutorial, I'll walk you through setting up your own space from scratch, so you can experience the same clarity and focus I did. Trust me, it's worth every minute. Ready to dive in? You can ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "start your free ClickUp account here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and follow along.",
            "marks": []
          }
