            "_type": "span",
            "text": "clickup.com",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". The signup is quick—you can use your Google or Apple account for speed. Once you're in, ClickUp guides you to create your first ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Workspace",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Think of this as your digital headquarters. Name it something clear, like \"My Business\" or \"Team Alpha.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-clickup"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You'll then answer a few questions about your role and team size. This helps ClickUp tailor the initial setup for you. Don't stress about the answers; you can change everything later. The genius of ClickUp is its flexibility. It adapts to how *you* work, not the other way around. For a deeper look at this foundational layer, check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is ClickUp?",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Understand and Structure Your Core Elements",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ClickUp is built on a simple hierarchy: ",
            "marks": []
          },
