            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/clickup-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start by creating one Space. I recommend \"Getting Started\" as a playground to test features. Inside, create a Folder and a List. Now, add a few tasks. This simple action is where the magic begins. Each task is a universe unto itself—you can add descriptions, subtasks, due dates, and assignees right from the start. To see how this structure plays out in real scenarios, these ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ClickUp use cases",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " are incredibly insightful.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
