        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ClickUp Docs:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Create rich-text documents right inside your Workspace. Link them to tasks, embed views, and collaborate in real-time. It's like having Google Docs married to your project management, without the tab switching. I draft all my content briefs here and link them directly to the writer's task.",
