        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automations & AI:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " This is the future. Go to any List or Folder and click \"Automations.\" You can set rules like \"When status changes to 'Done', move task to 'Archive' list\" or \"When a due date arrives, notify me in Slack.\" ClickUp's AI can even suggest automations or help you write task descriptions. The Business plan includes a generous 5,000 automations per month, making complex workflows hands-off. If you're moving from another tool, this ",
            "marks": []
          },
