            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is ClickUp really free forever?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes! ClickUp’s Free Forever plan is genuinely robust. It includes unlimited tasks, unlimited members, collaborative Docs, Kanban boards, Sprint Management, Calendar View, and 24/7 support. It’s not a time-limited trial; you can use it indefinitely for small teams and personal projects.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I switch from Asana, Trello, or Monday.com to ClickUp easily?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. ClickUp offers native import tools for Asana, Trello, Monday.com, Jira, and many others. You can bring over your tasks, projects, and often even comments and attachments with just a few clicks. Their help center has detailed guides for each migration.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What if I need help or get stuck?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ClickUp’s support is a standout. All plans, including Free, get 24/7 access to their support team via chat and email. They also have an extensive library of webinars, tutorials, and a community forum. For hands-on help, they offer a 100% money-back guarantee on paid plans if you’re not satisfied.",
